1
00:00:10,860 --> 00:00:12,780
♪The wind blows, but I don't see you♪

2
00:00:12,820 --> 00:00:14,740
♪I added a few more strokes♪

3
00:00:14,740 --> 00:00:17,380
♪To the ending♪

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:21,580
♪With the flowers falling
and the time passing♪

5
00:00:21,860 --> 00:00:24,140
♪Leaving only memories behind♪

6
00:00:24,300 --> 00:00:28,220
♪The wind blows from a long distance♪

7
00:00:28,340 --> 00:00:31,020
♪Yet, you didn't show up♪

8
00:00:31,140 --> 00:00:33,140
♪This love is full of regrets♪

9
00:00:33,300 --> 00:00:37,420
♪You are but a dream
in this fleeting life♪

10
00:00:40,260 --> 00:00:41,260
[Part For Ever]

11
00:00:41,260 --> 00:00:42,000
[Adapted from the novel by Jing Mo,]

12
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:42,900
[My Lord,
Madam Doesn't Want to See You Again]

13
00:00:42,900 --> 00:00:44,780
[Episode 19]

14
00:00:57,540 --> 00:01:03,340
♪People sit silently
by candlelight as night begins♪

15
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,510
Shameless!

16
00:01:09,040 --> 00:01:09,840
Wan'er,

17
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:12,120
you must take this medicine.

18
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:13,790
I'd do anything

19
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:15,280
to keep you healthy.

20
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:16,840
I know

21
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,870
that you see Commander Zhao as family,

22
00:01:19,590 --> 00:01:20,870
but I am also your husband.

23
00:01:22,590 --> 00:01:23,590
Do you truly believe

24
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:26,120
I'm as wicked and malicious?

25
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:28,920
But how do you explain
what happened that day?

26
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:30,870
That day, Commander Zhao...

27
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:32,590
Traitor!

28
00:01:32,590 --> 00:01:33,760
You killed my men.

29
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:35,510
I'll make you pay today!

30
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:41,640
Commander Zhao?

31
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:01,710
The way he reacted,

32
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,150
there was something going on.

33
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:04,840
Wan'er,

34
00:02:05,150 --> 00:02:06,200
give me three days.

35
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,350
I will uncover the truth

36
00:02:07,350 --> 00:02:08,310
and give you an explanation,

37
00:02:12,310 --> 00:02:13,120
all right?

38
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:15,870
Wan'er,

39
00:02:16,310 --> 00:02:17,470
please don't overthink this.

40
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:18,960
Take this medicine.

41
00:03:23,900 --> 00:03:27,660
♪The mountains and rivers
I've seen are painted on the fan♪

42
00:03:27,780 --> 00:03:31,140
♪The flowing clouds
embrace the wind and moon♪

43
00:03:31,300 --> 00:03:34,860
♪Longing immersed in the inkstone♪

44
00:03:35,020 --> 00:03:38,460
♪I foolishly think♪

45
00:03:38,740 --> 00:03:42,140
♪Unable to sleep, I was intoxicated
by the fragrance of books♪

46
00:03:42,260 --> 00:03:45,780
♪With you, the fragrance
fills the sky together♪

47
00:03:45,860 --> 00:03:51,700
♪Parting makes it hard
to express in many words♪

48
00:03:53,180 --> 00:03:56,740
♪I use tears to grind
the residual moon into the inkstone♪

49
00:03:57,020 --> 00:04:00,460
♪To write my longing
into every word and line♪

50
00:04:00,540 --> 00:04:03,580
♪The past of my soul is full of dreams♪

51
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,120
How is the investigation going?

52
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,360
[Tomb of Zhao Yi]
You were right, My Lord.

53
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,150
During the autopsy,

54
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:10,470
the coroner found traces of Wuchen
in Commander Zhao's body.

55
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,150
Combined with what Commander Zhao said,

56
00:04:12,150 --> 00:04:13,120
I deduced

57
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:15,280
that when he was trying
to seize Wang Zhen,

58
00:04:15,310 --> 00:04:16,480
in a desperate attempt to escape,

59
00:04:16,510 --> 00:04:17,680
Wang Zhen poisoned them.

60
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:20,360
But Commander Zhao managed to escape
with his martial prowess.

61
00:04:20,510 --> 00:04:21,560
When the poison took effect,

62
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:22,920
he mistook you for Wang Zhen.

63
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:24,870
Continue the pursuit.

64
00:04:25,190 --> 00:04:26,000
This time,

65
00:04:26,950 --> 00:04:28,510
we must capture him
and bring him to justice.

66
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:29,830
Yes, My Lord.

67
00:04:30,620 --> 00:04:34,540
[Tomb of Zhao Yi]

68
00:04:57,750 --> 00:04:59,560
I shouldn't have doubted you.

69
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,360
I'm sorry.

70
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:14,950
I've never blamed you.

71
00:05:17,310 --> 00:05:18,680
Stop staring at me.

72
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,510
I've been looking haggard lately.

73
00:05:20,750 --> 00:05:22,190
I haven't even combed my hair.

74
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:23,680
Let me help you.

75
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:42,560
There's a poem

76
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:43,920
that goes,

77
00:05:44,750 --> 00:05:45,750
"Pure water breeds the lotus,

78
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,510
natural grace needs no adornment."

79
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:48,310
It seems

80
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,680
to describe you perfectly.

81
00:05:51,070 --> 00:05:53,480
That's meant to describe
well-written prose.

82
00:05:54,950 --> 00:05:55,950
Let me try another one.

83
00:05:57,630 --> 00:05:59,720
"In the spring, she is granted
a bath in the Huaqing Pool.

84
00:06:00,390 --> 00:06:03,070
The hot spring water smooths
and cleanses her skin."

85
00:06:08,870 --> 00:06:10,510
Do you know the next line?

86
00:06:13,630 --> 00:06:16,510
"The maids help her up.
She looks delicate and pure."

87
00:06:18,630 --> 00:06:19,750
And what's the next line?

88
00:06:22,870 --> 00:06:24,920
What comes after that?

89
00:06:26,870 --> 00:06:28,000
You've got me stumped.

90
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,950
You know the answer to that.

91
00:06:50,620 --> 00:06:52,500
♪White dew penetrates the sandalwood♪

92
00:06:52,540 --> 00:06:54,180
♪Heading to the garden alone♪

93
00:06:54,220 --> 00:06:57,420
♪I play the Guqin among the trees♪

94
00:06:57,460 --> 00:06:59,220
♪And the cicadas chirp
deep in the bamboo courtyard♪

95
00:06:59,260 --> 00:07:02,180
♪A person inside a door♪

96
00:07:03,940 --> 00:07:07,460
♪As we see the falling leaves♪

97
00:07:07,540 --> 00:07:10,780
♪Threads of memories surround us

98
00:07:10,860 --> 00:07:14,820
♪They become a cocoon to wrap around us♪

99
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,360
Do I look beautiful today?

100
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:20,160
You're the most beautiful lady
I've ever seen.

101
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,600
Go.

102
00:07:23,630 --> 00:07:25,480
Deliver this letter
to the hot springs villa.

103
00:07:26,630 --> 00:07:27,480
Yes, My Lady.

104
00:07:29,070 --> 00:07:30,070
Are you sure?

105
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:34,120
Please allow me
to read your pulse again.

106
00:07:42,630 --> 00:07:43,870
It can't be wrong.

107
00:07:43,870 --> 00:07:44,950
You are pregnant.

108
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,830
Congratulations, My Lady.

109
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,120
Thank you, doctor.

110
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:57,830
This is the child of Ling Xiao and me.

111
00:07:59,190 --> 00:08:00,920
Ling Xiao and I have a child now.

112
00:08:03,510 --> 00:08:04,310
My Lady,

113
00:08:05,830 --> 00:08:07,310
His Lordship sent me
to deliver this letter to you.

114
00:08:11,020 --> 00:08:15,820
[To Su Wan'er]

115
00:08:22,100 --> 00:08:26,300
[Wan'er, I have some good news to tell you
at the City Lord's Mansion tonight.]

116
00:08:26,300 --> 00:08:29,300
[Please come. From Ling Xiao]

117
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:34,030
I can tell him this

118
00:08:34,270 --> 00:08:36,030
in person tonight.

119
00:08:40,140 --> 00:08:42,740
[Goodness and Virtue Bring Fragrance]

120
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:44,960
Hurry up.

121
00:08:45,510 --> 00:08:46,870
His Lordship and Miss Niyue's wedding

122
00:08:46,870 --> 00:08:48,120
is about to begin.

123
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,630
We don't want to miss
the auspicious timing.

124
00:08:49,630 --> 00:08:50,440
Easy.

125
00:08:50,870 --> 00:08:52,360
Whose wedding? What auspicious timing?

126
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:53,870
My Lady,

127
00:08:54,150 --> 00:08:55,360
the night is getting cold.

128
00:08:55,390 --> 00:08:56,440
Let me escort you back.

129
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:57,550
My Lady!

130
00:08:57,630 --> 00:08:58,440
My Lady!

131
00:09:07,670 --> 00:09:09,270
So, you called me here

132
00:09:10,390 --> 00:09:11,750
to share your joy.

133
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:19,480
Since you already know,

134
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,960
why embarrass yourself further?

135
00:09:25,270 --> 00:09:26,080
Ling Xiao,

136
00:09:26,750 --> 00:09:28,150
why are you doing this to me?

137
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,270
Do I need

138
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,360
to explain myself to you?

139
00:09:38,870 --> 00:09:40,440
What do you see me as?

140
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,630
A puppet

141
00:09:45,390 --> 00:09:47,080
or your plaything?

142
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:49,550
You tricked me

143
00:09:50,030 --> 00:09:52,360
and made me believe in you
wholeheartedly,

144
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,030
fall in love with you

145
00:09:54,790 --> 00:09:56,720
and dream of a future with you.

146
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:59,600
In the meantime,
you went to marry another,

147
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,960
trample on my dignity,

148
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,480
and play me like a fiddle.

149
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,510
I only had

150
00:10:09,510 --> 00:10:11,360
a fleeting interest in you.

151
00:10:12,670 --> 00:10:13,630
It's no fun

152
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,840
if you're getting serious.

153
00:10:23,510 --> 00:10:25,030
So, you admit it?

154
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:27,480
It was all a lie

155
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,870
the whole time?

156
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:34,550
Even Mr. Zhao's death

157
00:10:35,910 --> 00:10:37,630
was part of the deception?

158
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,360
He wanted to kill me,

159
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,910
so I had to send him on his way.

160
00:10:44,670 --> 00:10:47,030
Only you would fall
for such a simple trick.

161
00:10:49,630 --> 00:10:51,270
You made me fall in love with you,

162
00:10:52,390 --> 00:10:54,030
killed the people close to me,

163
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:56,440
and concealed it from me.

164
00:10:59,630 --> 00:11:00,440
Ling Xiao,

165
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:04,670
I only see your true colors now.

166
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:07,720
You're just a despicable scoundrel.

167
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:15,150
It's just a game of love
filled with fake feelings.

168
00:11:16,270 --> 00:11:17,480
Why are you taking it so seriously?

169
00:11:21,270 --> 00:11:22,080
Ling Xiao,

170
00:11:23,910 --> 00:11:25,240
I'm going to kill you!

171
00:11:25,660 --> 00:11:29,460
♪The wind blows, but I don't see you.
I added a few more strokes♪

172
00:11:29,580 --> 00:11:32,220
♪To the ending♪

173
00:11:33,390 --> 00:11:34,240
Ling!

174
00:11:36,670 --> 00:11:38,120
Ling, are you all right?

175
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:41,440
I'm fine.

176
00:11:43,670 --> 00:11:44,510
Su Wan'er,

177
00:11:44,750 --> 00:11:46,120
I thought we could
live harmoniously together

178
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,120
as sisters,

179
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:48,600
but you harbor resentment,

180
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:49,440
refuse to show your respect,

181
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,870
and even hurt Ling.

182
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,870
You want me to share my husband
with another woman?

183
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:56,510
Never!

184
00:11:57,790 --> 00:11:59,150
Su Wan'er, don't be shameless!

185
00:11:59,150 --> 00:11:59,870
Han Feng!

186
00:12:02,550 --> 00:12:04,120
Since you have no sense of tolerance,

187
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:05,720
from now on,

188
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,550
Niyue will be the wife,

189
00:12:10,030 --> 00:12:10,960
and you will be the concubine.

190
00:12:12,180 --> 00:12:18,700
♪This love is full of regrets.
You're a dream in this fleeting life♪

191
00:12:34,380 --> 00:12:41,660
♪A thousand journeys end,
transcending eternity♪

192
00:12:41,740 --> 00:12:48,300
♪Sounds of solitary mourning♪

193
00:12:49,220 --> 00:12:56,380
♪Life passes quickly,
like how dusk arrives suddenly♪

194
00:12:57,100 --> 00:13:02,980
♪The evening snowy wind
is too strong that the boat cannot sail♪

195
00:13:03,060 --> 00:13:10,420
♪The peach blossom falls on my bed,
the moon is as bright as ever♪

196
00:13:10,580 --> 00:13:17,820
♪With a bottle of wine by the river,
I sing softly♪

197
00:13:17,940 --> 00:13:21,540
♪Not going back, not looking back♪

198
00:13:21,660 --> 00:13:26,060
♪Even good times are spent in vain♪

199
00:13:26,820 --> 00:13:31,500
♪Trapped in the mornings
and the evenings♪

200
00:13:32,500 --> 00:13:35,300
♪As the flames of life
extinguish on a candle♪
